==Locked Transparency Options==
When locked transparency options are makred with an icon ( [[File:en/Manual/TransparencyOptions-a.png]] ), and are not affected by the '''X''' key. These options can still be toggled using clicking on the button, or using '''ctrl'''+('''1''' to '''9'''). These may be unlocked using '''ctrl'''+'''click''' on the appropriate buttons.